{"tid":2410204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳跨灣連接路預製雙拱鋼橋運抵本港","createTime":"2021-02-16T11:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T12:05:44.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d8d367283b45f9c76f5c08d6b57375b915e4ff","tid":2410204,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"將軍澳跨灣連接路預製雙拱鋼橋運抵本港<br />\n2021-02-16 HKT 18:39<br />\n<br />\n&quot;將軍澳跨灣連接路的預製雙拱鋼橋運抵本港，早上進入將軍澳灣，將於稍後在橋墩位置安裝......<br />\n<br />\n......將軍澳跨灣連接路橫跨將軍澳灣，連接將軍澳東南部和將軍澳&mdash;藍田隧道，亦會連繫調景嶺和將軍澳市中心。項目預期於2022年竣工，屆時往返將軍澳東南部和九龍將更為便捷，亦可分流環保大道及將軍澳市中心一帶的交通。 &quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575910-20210216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575910-20210216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=9628c70c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575910-20210216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7ae68733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575910-20210216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b005a1067f6758882a280bdaa2f27f89144cd065","tid":2410204,"uid":70488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"咁又點"},{"pid":"99a9c35f3c4831b6d54f79ecd83cb1d5fb8d09e0","tid":2410204,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b005a1067f6758882a280bdaa2f27f89144cd065","tid":2410204,"uid":70488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"咁又點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"支那製造小心"}]}